"Carnage, Dark One, Skywarp, Ramjet, Dirge, Terrorsaur, Cyber Claw, Ultracon, 
Stegotron, Triceradon, Sludge, Swoop, Snarl, Slag, Grimlock, Dinobot, Iron 
Raptor, join me in my quest. I will reward you greatly. I will not ask you to 
destroy your leaders. Simply to join me in my quest. Cybertron will be ours. 
I will allow the Factions to continue to function on Cybertron, but they will 
be monitored." Magmatron sent his signal again. He didn't have much luck with 
them before. Maybe he will this time. "And one last thing, Megatron this goes 
out to you: The Ark Key is destroyed. Hell Beast did it. It would have been 
your only real chance to destroy it. Please accept my humble apoligies for 
not getting here earlier, I might have been able to stop him."
